research_municipality_step.notes: Humble, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government, which is categorized as 'mayor_council' for this response. The City Council consists of the Mayor and five Council Members elected by place. The City Manager and City Secretary are appointed positions and thus not included as elected officials. There was conflicting information regarding Council Member Place 5, but the most recent agenda indicates Rick Swanson was administered the oath of office for Place 5.
